org.apache.ignite.ml.environment.deploy

Interface DeployingContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeployingContextImpl

    public interface DeployingContext
    Class represents user's class loading environment for specific remote job. This contexst is used to determine class loader for missing classes on worker node.
